Praise Oghenefejiro Idamadudu (amụrụ na 18 Disemba 1998) bụ nwanyị Naijiriịa na-agba ọsọ na-agba ịnyịnya na mita 200 na mita 400
Ọ bụ onye nwetara ọlaọcha na 4 × 400 mita relay na 2018 Commonwealth Games.

A mụrụ ya na Ovu, Delta Steetị, o mere nke mbụ ya na mba ụwa na 2014 African Youth Games, ebe ọ bụ onye nwetara ọla edo 200m. Ka e mesịrị n'afọ ahụ, ọ gara asọmpi na 2014 World Junior Championships in Athletics na 200, 400 na 4 × 400 mita relay

Ọ ga-asọ mpi maka Naijirịa na 2014 Summer Youth Olympics, mana a manyere ṅdị otu ahụ niile ka ha pụọ n'ihi nchegbu banyere ọrịa Ebola nke West Africa. Na 2015 African Junior Athletics Championships ọ bụ onye nwetara ọla edo abụọ (200 m na 4 × 400 m relay) mana onye South Africa bụ Nicola de Bruyn meriri ya na nke abụọ na 200 m na 2015 African Youth Athletics Championship. O ji ihe nrite ọla edo atọ mechie afọ ahụ na Commonwealth Youth Games, na-ewere 200m na utu aha relay abụọ.

Idamadudu nwetara ọkwa mba mbụ ya na 200m na 2015 Nigerian Athletics Championships. Egwuregwu ya n'afọ ahụ mere ka e jiri ya tụnyere onye ṅwetara ihe nrite Olympic Falilat Ogunkoya site na mgbasa ozi mba. Ọ hapụrụ akụkụ nke oge 2016 n'ihi mmerụ ahụ n'ikpere. O mekwara asọmpi na 2017, nke oge ya pụtara ìhè bụ onye nke abụọ ṅa 200m na asọmpi mba. Idamadudu mere ṅke mbụ ya na mba ụwa na 2018 Commonwealth Games, na-eru 200m semi-final ma na-ekerịta na 4 × 400 mita relay ọlaọcha nrite na Yinka Ajayi, Patience Okon George na Glory Onome Nathaniel.
